{"tid":2270334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Now新聞台】拜登如果今次成功當選，將以78歲高齡成為美國史上年紀最大的總統。","createTime":"2020-11-04T03:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T04:50:10.000Z","uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7b4b2bb62a4562830c498e83a94af403062cbd","tid":2270334,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=411569&amp;catCode=123&amp;topicId=1039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411569%26catCode%3D123%26topicId%3D1039&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=a08c802c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411569%26catCode%3D123%26topicId%3D1039&h=a8d48293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=411569&amp;catCode=123&amp;topicId=1039</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【Now新聞台】做過副總統的拜登縱橫美國政壇半世紀，如果今次成功當選，將以78歲高齡成為美國史上年紀最大的總統。<br />\n<br />\n拜登：「他（特朗普）將會徹底改變這個國家的特質，我無法袖手旁觀。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n之前兩度參選總統，但連民主黨內初選都未能勝出的拜登，去年為了特朗普捲土重來。<br />\n<br />\n拜登在賓夕法尼亞州出生，完成法律學位後，很快便踏入政壇，進入特拉華州紐卡斯爾縣議會，年僅29歲便當選聯邦參議員，一當就當了36年，期間出任過參議院外交關係委員會主席、司法委員會主席。<br />\n<br />\n2008年大選，奧巴馬看中拜登熟悉國會議事程序，擅長外交和國安議題，邀請他擔任副手。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的仕途發展順遂，但人生遭遇過重大打擊。72年首次當選參議員後，短短數星期，第一任妻子和小女兒遇車禍身亡；2015年，被視為特拉華州州長熱門人選的長子博拜登因為腦癌逝世，年僅46歲。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>拜登以堅韌的態度面對人生，晚年第三度參選總統，在經濟、處理疫情和法治等方面爭取選民信任。</strong><br />\n拜登以堅韌的態度面對人生，晚年第三度參選總統，在經濟、處理疫情和法治等方面爭取選民信任。"},{"pid":"7b17c9a91e281ad1e8610e04262d8991e619bf09","tid":2270334,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"登登<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fcd348774fc1fdb1f0aec62feaf91b8c3e4745","tid":2270334,"uid":273716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"Now咁樣玩鳩香港班藍屍都有既<br />\n一起一伏好易爆血管<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e9330adf992cde9ccc844629f0c0c51863a0d5","tid":2270334,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"三度參選不果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cca7c5d6b48aa0d38e5fe3bbe6c76a144af791","tid":2270334,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"我都有睇<br />\n一面倒唱好拜登<br />\ntrump 完全唔提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要搵袁彌昌上去講野 講勁撚耐<br />\ntitle 戰略分析師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話有知識水平既人先投biden<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb20f955b72f52583b38a4ad5aa7e63b306a709","tid":2270334,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"登登贏面好高"},{"pid":"f26718b33c69432f61db570f50db13e3463cebd5","tid":2270334,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:05:51.000Z","msg":"幻登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf8ccc305726cbe735fed8926b0b7ec4f119acd","tid":2270334,"uid":364767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"我啋！ 咁老仲咁咸濕，真係該煨囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUTr_mtWoAUGYEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEUTr_mtWoA